From: Feras Daoud <ferasda@mellanox.com>
Date: Tue, 31 Oct 2017 14:03:12 +0200
Subject: net/mlx5e: IPoIB, Add ethtool support to get child time stamping
 parameters
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc1
Git-commit: 93b66472ce73920795f1477729620cce38fe34c0
References: bsc#1103990 FATE#326006

Add support to get time stamping capabilities using ethtool for
child interface.
Usage example:
	ethtool -T CHILD-DEVNAME

This change reuses the functionality of parent devices and does not
introduce any new logic.

Signed-off-by: Feras Daoud <ferasda@mellanox.com>
Signed-off-by: Saeed Mahameed <saeedm@mellanox.com>
Acked-by: Thomas Bogendoerfer <tbogendoerfer@suse.de>
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/mellanox/mlx5/core/ipoib/ethtool.c |    1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/mellanox/mlx5/core/ipoib/ethtool.c
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/mellanox/mlx5/core/ipoib/ethtool.c
@@ -254,4 +254,5 @@ const struct ethtool_ops mlx5i_ethtool_o
 const struct ethtool_ops mlx5i_pkey_ethtool_ops = {
 	.get_drvinfo        = mlx5i_get_drvinfo,
 	.get_link           = ethtool_op_get_link,
+	.get_ts_info        = mlx5i_get_ts_info,
 };
